articles.title: Uttarakhand: Dozens missing in Indian Himalayas avalanche - BBC.com
articles.description: At least 25 people are still missing in a remote part of the country's north.
articles.content:
At least 25 road workers remain trapped after a massive avalanche struck a remote border area in the northern Indian state of Uttarakhand, officials say.
